Wait for it!!! 😍 The makings of a fluffy omelette cannot be missed! 😍🙌🏼❤️
Follow @hungryhugh for more food! 🙌🏼 Checkout my Snapchat 👻: HungryHugh!
🍳
🍴: Omurice
👉🏼: @kichikichi_kyoto
📍: Kichikichi,中京区材木町185-4
Kyoto, 京都府 〒604-8017 Japan
🍚
@kichikichi_kyoto’s OMURICE (open omelette over fried rice) is one of the best dishes I’ve had here in Kyoto! The omelette is fluffy, the fried rice has tons of flavor and that special sauce will make your eyes roll back! 😂👌🏼😍 Thank you @hulagirl7 for all your help! 😘❤️
.
